==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insolubility
<hw>In*sol`u*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>insolubilitas</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>insolubilit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality or state of being insoluble or not
dissolvable, as in a fluid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quality of being inexplicable or
insolvable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insoluble</ent>⟦br⟧
